query-joined_table: FROM test.get_all_neap tsm left JOIN test.xbi_geolocation eoc_2 ON tsm.location_code  = eoc_2.code left JOIN test.xbi_campaign eoc_3 ON (tsm.ActivityID  = eoc_3.campaign_ActivityID_old And tsm.Yr = eoc_3.campaign_Yr)
